<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Line 155 of Zend/Db/Table/Select.php does not use the table's schema when building the FROM part of select query.</p>

<p>$name = $info[Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::NAME];</p>

<p>should be:</p>

<p>$name = $info[Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::SCHEMA] ? 
    $info[Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::SCHEMA] . '.' . $info[Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::NAME] : 
    $info[Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::NAME];</p>

